response.overview: While surfing on a secluded beach, Nancy finds herself in the feeding grounds of a great white shark. Though stranded only 200 yards from shore, survival proves to be the ultimate test of wills, requiring all of her ingenuity, resourcefulness, and fortitude.
response.tagline: What was once in the deep is now in the shallows.
response.title: The Shallows

titles.title: The Shallows: Gefahr aus der Tiefe
